<abstract>
<section>
<para>Total Chlorophyll concentration of Lake Candia (Northern Italy), collected by CNR Institute of Ecosystem Study. This parameter is collected from 1986 until now at different depth (surface, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6 m depth), and like an integrated water sample from 0 to 6 meters. The concentration is calculated according to the fluorimetric analysis and methanol extraction.</para>
</section>
